snippet.title: Jane's Combat Simulations: Advanced Tactical Fighters - Gold (1997) - Teaser
snippet.description:
Official trailer for Jane's Combat Simulations: Advanced Tactical Fighters - Gold by Electronic Arts.

Previously removed from YouTube after the account owner threw in the towel for no apparent reason (not DMCAs). Of course, re-encoding made the quality dip further.
